{"type": "article", "id": 28761, "title": "可穿戴低音炮", "description": "", "date": "2016-06-28T06:53:19Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 3, "praise_count": 35, "image": "img/article/article_show/201607031215312zaLgt6CJQPMy8BE.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>          </p>\n<p>出门在外该如何享受震撼的音乐体验？德国初创公司 Lofelt 最近研发了全球第一款可穿戴的低音炮 BASSLET，它就好像是一块手表，可以戴在手腕上。小巧的外型中内置了一套完整的音响系统，其中就有 Lofelt 自主研发的 LoSound 引擎。不同于其他通过蓝牙连接的设备，只要可以发声，哪怕是一台老旧的 Walkman 都能够与 BASSLET 相连，带来沉浸式的音乐体验。你可以通过<a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/basslet/the-basslet-a-wearable-subwoofer-for-your-body\">链接</a>参与众筹，最低价为 139 欧元。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703121529NxzqFbheLSd64R0P.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.56030534\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607031215293scNhVbUwMLI9zBe.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.56323529\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703121530FMITESH1RUbAdo6Y.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.53139357\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703121530EWFZ8VpqYB50yScr.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.48823529\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n\n"}